events.name: ゴブリン討伐　ラスト

parameters:
\n<Serena>...I can't find anything. Was it just my
imagination...?

\n<Serena>Wha...t... A green, infant... A goblin baby? This
is...
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Goblin Baby: Agi... Agigi...

\n<Serena>Ugh, uuu... Wha, what...! Just looking at it...
makes my chest feel uneasy...!
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Goblin Baby: Gii-...!
\n<Serena>No, no way...!
\n<Serena>Ha-... I ended up running away without thinking...

\n<Serena>Even though it's just a powerless infant, the mere
fact that it resembles a human makes it feel so
repulsive...

\n<Serena>Extermination... is it... okay...? After all, a
single one won't survive for long.
\n<Serena>Rather, I don't want to go back to the hut...

\n<Serena>However, if I return without proof of subjugation
again, the Master will scold me...
\n<Serena>No, I did make an effort. Indeed.
\n<Serena>An effort, indeed.
\n<Guild Master>Yes... yes. I thought as much...
\V[2501]\n<Serena>Good, good. With this, the matter is settled.
'　ゴブリン討伐は完了だ。宿に帰って休もう。'
'クエストをクリアした。'
回想セーブ 温泉街ゴブリン敗北
Mmm, huh... Hah!?\n<Serena>
Gyii! Gyiii!\n<Goblin>
Eek!?\n<Serena>
W-what is this situation...!?\n<Serena>

(Dragged into a nest...? Pinned down by goblins...
There are roughly seven of them around...)\n<Serena>

The ring is here... If only I could generate the
Afa-Bile...\n<Serena>
Gugya!\n<Goblin>
Stop it! Don't pull!!\n<Serena>
Stop, stop--\n<Serena>
Gegya!\n<Goblin>
Aaahhh! My clothes...! Let go! Don't look!!\n<Serena>

(Damn it... My concentration... is disrupted...!
Because of something like this... I can't
regenerate my equipment...!)\n<Serena>
Gihehehe...\n<Goblin>
*panting*...?\n<Serena>
!?... What are you rubbing against me?!\n<Serena>
It's disgusting...! No...!\n<Serena>
Gyuhhe... Gihh...\n<Goblin>
Hii...!?\n<Serena>
Ah... uh... ah...!\n<Serena>

What is this... It's not an attack... What am I
being subjected to... What are the goblins
doing...?\n<Serena>
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
...\n<Goblin>

Stop it... Don't bring "that" any closer to me...
It's something very vile...!\n<Serena>
(It seems like something I shouldn't see...!)\n<Serena>
Get away! Let go... Stop it... ugh!?\n<Serena>
Noooooo!?\n<Serena>
No! No! Not there...!\n<Serena>
Pushing, pressing against me...! Eh!? No...!\n<Serena>
Gihi... Gi!\n<Goblin>
!投擲物1
!投擲物1
エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1

Oh la la! Goblins! Getting it on in broad
daylight!\n<Erika>
Ah... Erika-sama...!?\n<Serena>
Oh? Who do I find here but Serena!\n<Erika>

Seriously, that was a close shave if I ever saw
one!\n<Erika>

Can't be helped then! Consider this a favor I'm
doing for you!\n<Erika>

Ah-tch, ptooey... Damn goblins are so damn
slimy...!\n<Erika>
Serena, are you alright?\n<Erika>

I'm fine. My apologies, Erika-sama... I owe you
one.\n<Serena>

Be more careful. Even weaklings like them have the
strength to kill a human.\n<Erika>
It's a lesson learned.\n<Serena>

Alright. Shall we head back? ...But not in that
state, obviously.\n<Erika>

I'll go look for some clothes or cloth you can
wrap yourself in.\n<Erika>
My apologies...\n<Serena>
Phew...\n<Serena>
What... was that, I wonder...\n<Serena>
It was scary...\n<Serena>

It was a different kind of fear, not just pain or
the fear of death...\n<Serena>

It feels like it will haunt my dreams. I doubt
I'll be able to forget it for a while...\n<Serena>
Scene_Recollection.prototype.rngd_exit_scene();
Sounds like you had quite the ordeal.\n<Guild Master>
Indeed... I have no face to show.\n<Serena>

How about it? Had enough of being an adventurer?
It's painful, dangerous, and to top it off,
stinks.\n<Guild Master>
...\n<Serena>
No, it's not a problem.\n<Serena>

Certainly, there was fear. I may have
underestimated things.\n<Serena>

But what I must do lies ahead. If so, then I shall
proceed. There's nothing to do but continue.\n<Serena>
Tch.\n<Guild Master>

Well... at least the goblins are gone now.
Consider the quest complete.\n<Guild Master>

Here, your reward. Go get some sleep, eat, and
take a bath.\n<Guild Master>
...\n<Serena>
\V[2501]\n<Serena>...Is this the end of the matter then.
'　危うい所だったが、なんとか依頼は完了した。'
'　今日はもう帰って休もう…。'
'ゴブリンに負けた'
